snippet.title: Whisker Squadron: Survivor - Six One Indie Showcase Trailer
snippet.description: Join a ragtag crew of feline pilots in a dramatic showdown against corporate-powered robots called The Swarm. Take another look at Whisker Squadron: Survivor in this trailer for the roguelike shooter game from the creators of Race the Sun. Whisker Squadron: Survivor is available now on Steam.
